text: Shinji Tatsuta (born 23 December 1914) was a Japanese ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1914 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Japanese male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Japan Category:Ski jumpers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Hokkaido
